<br>
I have a question to those who come here. While walking through Befallen, i came across one of the most interesting of Clerics. He actually pondered if he could convert me to the god he prayed to.. which incidently was one of the Marr's. Please dont be angered if i do not remember, but i just do not see them as.. anything equivalent to the one i have sworn to follow.<br>
<br>
She pauses for a moment, looking around a little more.<br>
<br>
Does this happen often ? Will i have to live with constant attempts to sway the beliefs i have, just because people cannot fathom that a human might not follow the path of love, despite being neither Necromancer nor Shadow knight ?<br>
<br>
She sits back, grabs a mug of ale and sips on it while waiting for any answers that might come.<br>
